quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,23,"Hino e gom…óim…ďe …ďen, wor…ďe hunnu…ďe ko ahodi kon e Alla, …ďe hunni ahadi ma…ď…ďe tabital e mu√Īal ngal ka ha…ďugol fii Alla. Wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe waraama maa sahodini e laawol Alla, wo…ó…ďe goo e ma…ď…ďe, hino habbii sahodinde fii Alla. ∆Āen gom…óim…ďe mee…óaali wa…ótitude ko …ďe ahodi kon e Alla, wano naafiqii…ďe …ďen firtirnoo ahadiiji ma…ď…ďe non."
  33,24,"∆äum, ko fii yo Alla yo…ďir goongu…ďe …ďen, ko …ďe hunniri ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin e Alla kon, …ďe hunni kala ahadi ma…ď…ďe. E fii no O leptira naafiqii…ďe firtu…ďe ahadiiji mun …óin, si Mo yi…ói, wano warugol …ďe hara …ďe tuubaali e keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum O ja…ďana …ďe tuubuubuyee. Tawde pellet, Alla siforii Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e junuubi mun, Hinnoto…óo ontigi."
  33,25,"Alla ruttidii Qurayshi e GhaŠĻ≠afaan, e kala jokku…ďe …ďe, wonndude e tikkere ma…ď…ďe nden e suno, tawde …ďe waawali mehugol fii gom…óim…ďe …ďen. Alla non yonii gom…óim…ďe …ďen ko …ďe ha…ďida e ma…ď…ďe, tawde O wurtuno henndu, O jippini Malaa'ika. Alla siforii Cemmbe, Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa hoyfina."
  33,26,"Alla jippini …ďen wallindirnoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe, jeyaa…ďe e Alyahuuda'en, e tataaji ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe da…ónodraynoo e ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe, O weddii kulol e pittaali ma…ď…ďe; tawi onon gom…óim…ďe …ďen, hi…óon wara fedde e ma…ď…ďe, dahon fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe."
  33,27,"Alla jeytini on …ďaawo halkeede …ďe, leydi ma…ď…ďe ndin e ko woni e mayri, immorde e remuru e le…ó…óe tamaro. O jeytini on kadi galleeji ma…ď…ďe e jawdi ma…ď…ďe, O jeytini on leydi Khaybar ndi mee…óaano tippude e mun, kono on tippay e mayri. ∆äum ko fodoore e wewlinir…óum gom…óim…ďe …ďen. Alla siforii hattan…óo kala huunde. Huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  33,28,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Maakan suddii…ďe maa …ďen, …ďaawo …ďe …óa…ď…ďirde ma ya√Ī√Īangol …ďe nafaqe ndin, tawi non a maraa feere mun: Si wonii ko nguurndam aduna faala…óon e cu…óaari majjam, haray aree e am, mi dakmitira on no seera…óo dakmitirtee ado cergal ngal, mi seera on ontuma, cergal ngal lorra alaa e mu'un."
  33,29,"Si tawii non ko welayee Alla on e Nulaa…óo Makko on faala…óon, e Aljanna on ka galle laakara, haray mu√Ī√Īodee e fiyaaku mon on, tawde pellet, Alla maranii kala mo∆ī∆īin…óo mu√Īal mun e gonndigal mon e moo…óon, noji…ďdi mawndi."
  33,30,"Ko onon yo suddii…ďe Annabiijo on! Kala addu…óo e moo…óon goopo …ďanngungol, o sowante lepte …óen √Ďalnde Darngal, cowalle …ói…ói, sabu maqaamu e teddungal makko ngal, e fii la…ď…ďingol Annabiijo Alla on (yo o his). Ngol sowugol …óen lepte, wonii ko newanii Alla."